The latest forum bringing together human resource professionals in the hospitality industry was held at the Panari Hotel, Nairobi recently.Guest speaker Skills Global managing partner Benson Mwangi spoke on emotional intelligence in HR management.These forums, now on it s seventh edition, were initiated by Angela Mwenderani, Tune Hotels HR, training and development manager together with event organiser 24:7 CEO Duncan Gwaro.The aim of the forum is to give human resource professionals an avenue to network.